text: The Yunnan lake newt (Cynops wolterstorffi) was a species of newts. It was part of the family Salamandridae. It was also known as Wolterstorff's newt. It used to live in China. ==References== * Datong, Y. & Lau, M.W.N. 2004. Cynops wolterstorffi . 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Category:Newts Category:Animals of Asia
title: Yunnan lake newt
